        "Cognito",
        "UserPool"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Authentication子图建好了，包含Cognito和UserPool，用实线相连。接下来API层您希望怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Authentication",
        "Cognito",
        "UserPool",
        "APIGW",
        "Auth",
        "Lambda"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "API层需要三个组件：APIGW作为入口，中间加一个Auth节点专门做令牌校验，然后Lambda执行业务。APIGW连Auth，Auth再连Lambda，形成调用链。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIGW",
        "Auth",
        "Lambda",
        "API Layer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里的Auth节点和Authentication子图是什么关系？User Pool和Auth之间需要连线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserPool",
        "Auth",
        "Authentication",
        "API Layer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "关键问题。User Pool负责颁发令牌，Auth节点负责校验令牌，它们之间是虚线关系，标注\"Validates tokens\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserPool",
        "Auth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加虚线连接和标注。现在画客户端部分，您用什么工具模拟调用？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Postman"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
